title: The Walk (2015) English Subtitles for French Parts
description:
These are English Subtitles for the French dialogue of the movie.

I used 2 current subtitle sources to piece together this. Subtitles may not be perfect and the translations may not be great.

Subtitles may or may not be out of sync in some places.I am not French speaking so I do not know if some subs are correct or not but it seems the majority of the subs are very close or right on. 

This is probably the best you will get until someone creates something better or the subtitles from the Blu-Ray/DVD are released. I have skimmed through some parts and those parts made sense so I guess it this can't be too bad. Enjoy!
